                    - @Localizer["Wallet file is stored locally, log in via password"]<br />
                </p>
                <p class="info">
                    @Localizer["Supported Languages"]: @Localizer["English/Chinese"]<br />
                    @Localizer["Supported OS"]: Android 5 @Localizer["or later"]<br />
                </p>
                <p class="down-time">2017-12-5</p>
                <a class="down-btn" href="@Localizer["https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=neo.app"]" target="_blank">@Localizer["Open Google Play"]</a>
            </li>
            <li class="down-box">
                <img src="~/images/download/down-O3.jpg" />
                <h2>O3 - Neo Wallet<small>0.1.1</small></h2>
